  "scoringRules": [
    "Ranking is a preview aid for admin review, not an automatic assignment decision.",
    "Scores must be scoped by tenantId and projectId.",
    "Scores must be calculated from source-safe operational metrics and stable refs.",
    "Do not use raw identity, bank, contact, health, age, gender, religion or family data.",
    "Do not use payment amount as a proxy for quality.",
    "A shopper with insufficient sample size must not be ranked as better or worse without manual review.",
    "A shopper with conflicting assignment, visit or review signals must be marked conflict_review_required.",
    "Manual admin adjustment requires reason and reviewer reference.",
    "Ranking must show metric breakdown and not only a final score."
  ],
