    "Ranking UI must show it is preview/admin aid, not automatic assignment.",
    "Show metric breakdown and reasons, not only top score.",
    "Show insufficient sample and conflict review states.",
    "Do not expose raw identity, contact, bank, private communication or sensitive attributes.",
    "Do not rank globally across tenants/projects unless explicitly filtered and documented.",
